{"blogid": "118522653", "writerAge": "码龄3年", "writerBlogNum": "114", "writerCollect": "198", "writerComment": "115", "writerFan": "579", "writerGrade": "4级", "writerIntegral": "1573", "writerName": "dudududu--", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_118522653.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "659754", "writerRankWeekly": "278665", "writerThumb": "105", "writerVisitNum": "36036", "blog_read_count": "7428", "blog_time": "于 2021-07-06 15:58:53 发布", "blog_title": "linux后台运行任务命令(nohup: 忽略输入并把输出追加到“nohup.out“)", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<p>比如，有一个任务，在服务器要执行</p>\n<pre><code>php worker.php\n</code></pre>\n<p>这个命令是挂起的，总不能一直这样挂起。<br/> 为了不影响其它操作，我们把它后台执行。</p>\n<pre><code>nohup php worker.php &amp;\n按enter\n</code></pre>\n<p>这样就OK了</p>\n<p>执行nohup php artisan command:worker &amp;提示如下：<br/> nohup: 忽略输入并把输出追加到\"nohup.out\"</p>\n<p>不要使用之前的nohup php worker.php &amp;<br/> 改用<br/> nohup php worker.php &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp; 就OK啦</p>\n<p>如果还有问题，那么就php worker.php<br/> 看他的报错，进行修改！！<br/> 直到没有报错：nohup php worker.php &amp;<br/> ps ax | grep 进程<br/> 查看存在worker就好了！！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\20210706155817765.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\20210706155822297.png\"/></p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "PHP", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "